      • setValueAt

        public void setValueAt(java.lang.Object aValue,
                       int rowIndex,
                       int columnIndex,
                       boolean notifyListeners)
        Sets the value in the cell at columnIndex and rowIndex to aValue. This method allows to choose will the model listeners notified or not.
        Parameters:
        aValue - the new value
        rowIndex - the row whose value is to be changed
        columnIndex - the column whose value is to be changed
        notifyListeners - indicates whether the model listeners are notified
